title: DarkSpectre Malicious Browser Extension C2 Activity & Exfil
id: 48708881-7a40-4f15-86a5-9248621ebf7d
status: experimental
description:
  Detects network connections to domains associated with the DarkSpectre threat
  actor's campaigns, including GhostPoster, ShadyPanda, and The Zoom Stealer.
  These campaigns leverage malicious browser extensions for data theft,
  affiliate fraud, and corporate espionage.
references:
